      <description>&lt;p&gt;A simple cooking setup keeps food costs low and gives you more control on long trips.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Best Budget Cooking Gear&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;best-budget-cooking-gear&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#best-budget-cooking-gear&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Gas One Dual Fuel Stove&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;gas-one-dual-fuel-stove&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#gas-one-dual-fuel-stove&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: works with propane and butane, easy to refuel.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: open-flame use requires good ventilation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Check Stove Price&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Stanley Adventure Cook Set&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;stanley-adventure-cook-set&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#stanley-adventure-cook-set&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: compact nesting design, durable for daily use.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: limited capacity for two-plus people.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;View Stanley Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Lodge 10.25&amp;quot; Cast Iron Skillet&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;lodge-1025-cast-iron-skillet&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#lodge-1025-cast-iron-skillet&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: versatile and nearly indestructible.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: heavier than non-stick alternatives.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Shop Lodge Skillet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;BougeRV 12V Fridge (small models)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;bougerv-12v-fridge-small-models&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#bougerv-12v-fridge-small-models&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: reduces grocery waste, efficient on DC power.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: entry models have tighter storage space.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;See BougeRV Options&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
